name: Video 4
description: mCherry-cro BSC-40 cells were infected at a MOI = 5 with a virus encoding YFP-tagged to the A5 protein (VACV-A5-YFP), and tracked using live cell microscopy to detect the appearance of late stage A5-YFP protein.
